Ways To Cheat:<br>
Ways people cheat are not losing enough force, never let your opponet lose force in chunks make him count it and if you don&#146;t believe him count it yourself. Big power battles, If your opponet seems to have to haigh of a power in a game count it yourself, you don&#146;t have to believe him. Missing hand, don&#146;t let your opponet put his hand down next to his other piles he will then lift up all the piles trying to find his hand and may not even end up with the same hand. Shuffle cut and replace. Always cut your opponets deck after he looks through it, there is no excuse for not doing it so just do it. <br>
